  <div class="container">
  <div class="row">

<h1>Office Robot In the Cloud</h3>

<% unless current_user %>
  <ul>
    <li><h3><%= link_to "Sign Up Page", new_user_registration_path %></h3></li>
    <li><h3><%= link_to "Sign In Page", new_user_session_path %></h3></li>
  </ul>

  <p>Welcome to the Panhandle Door Office Robot in the cloud.  For now, all the Office Robot has to offer is various Allmoxy Tools.</p>
